    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Meant for quick strikes and slashes, this long, slender knife is incredibly sharp along one edge.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/races/other-races/featured-races/arg-drow\">Drow</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/hybrid-classes/swashbuckler\">swashbucklers</a>&nbsp;and assassins are particularly fond of these weapons.</em></p>\n<p>A confirmed&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Critical-Hits\">critical hit</a>&nbsp;or successful&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/rogue#TOC-Sneak-Attack\">sneak attack</a>&nbsp;with a drow razor deals an additional 2 points of damage; this damage is precision damage and is not multiplied on a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Critical-Hits\">critical hit</a>. A character with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/races/other-races/featured-races/arg-drow\">drowâ€™s</a>&nbsp;weapon familiarity racial trait treats the drow razor as a martial weapon.</p>",
